  {
    "fnNumber": "47",
    "fnHTML": "<p>The eight spheres of mastery (<span lang='pi'>aṭṭha abhibha-āyatana</span>) are found in <span class='sclinktext'>DN&#8239;16<span class='scsegments'>:3.24.1–3.32.6</span></span>, <span class='sclinktext'>DN&#8239;33<span class='scsegments'>:3.1.142–3.1.67</span></span>, <span class='sclinktext'>DN&#8239;34<span class='scsegments'>:2.1.159–2.1.189</span></span>, <span class='sclinktext'>MN&#8239;77<span class='scsegments'>:23.1–23.33</span></span>, <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.439</span> (<span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.440</span>, <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.441</span>, <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.442</span>, <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.443</span>, <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.444</span>, <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.445</span>, <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;1.446</span>), <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;8.65</span>, and <span class='sclinktext'>AN&#8239;10.29<span class='scsegments'>:6.1–13.6</span></span>. Compare <span class='sclinktext'>MN&#8239;128</span>.</p>"
